{"data":{"allProjectsJson":{"sections":[{"button":{"label":"Visit me on Github","url":"https://github.com/victor-jvp","visible":false},"projects":[{"category":"🐃 ISEI PymeSoft","description":"Pymesoft is a comprehensive organizational management suite designed to streamline how businesses track innovation, performance, and strategic goals. By centralizing key areas such as performance indicators, project evaluations, and operational commitments, the platform provides leadership with a clear, real-time overview of the company's progress and health. It simplifies the transition from planning to execution through automated reporting and integrated meeting management, ensuring that teams stay focused on high-impact activities while fostering a culture of accountability and continuous improvement across the entire organization.","image":{"alt":"ISEI Pymesoft Project","linkTo":null,"src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/740b9/pymesoft.png","srcSet":"/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/7c4d4/pymesoft.png 100w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/6e056/pymesoft.png 200w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/740b9/pymesoft.png 400w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/f5d30/pymesoft.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/e52fc/pymesoft.webp 100w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/b7b52/pymesoft.webp 200w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/6a72a/pymesoft.webp 400w,\n/static/31973ee8db1a85580be56932ba1dce17/a9cee/pymesoft.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":224}}},"objectFit":null},"links":[],"tags":["Laravel","Vue3","Inertia JS","MariaDB","Bootstrap"],"title":"Evaluations, Indicators and Services","visible":true},{"category":"🐃 AED-SGS Service Requirement